Author: cosmicintegral7
Title: [ICO] BeefCoin - Integrated production of organic beef from farm to table
Body: First of all my apologies for asking a factual question regarding the man behind this project. I thought  Mr.Denis Sukhotin founded FxPro. There are no online documents which suggest other wise. Can you please help me with any links or documents supporting the claim that Mr. Mr. Nikolay Melbard is one of the co founder of FxPro , as claimed in the video/medium posts?  Medium Post : https://medium.com/@BeefCoin/the-story-of-nikolay-melbard-ac83b80d1abd  Thise medium post from Mr.Nikolay Melbard says he along with friends co founded it in 2000.But as per FXPro official website it was founded in 2006. https://www.fxpro.co.uk/group/company  Kindly request you to clarify on these questions.

Author: Beef Coin
Title: [ICO] BeefCoin - Integrated production of organic beef from farm to table
Body: You are right, FxPro was founded in 2006, it is misprint in Medum post, we fixed it.  Regarding your question, FxPro was co-founded by several people which also were co-authors of book about Forex trading: https://www.ozon.ru/context/detail/id/28271426/  Denis Sukhotin, Pavel Novikov, Nikolay Melbard, Alexey Shilov among them.

Author: Beef Coin
Title: [ICO] BeefCoin - Integrated production of organic beef from farm to table
Body: Unlike many other ICOs that have only idea without any MVP, our project is really existing and profitable business.  We have a big agricultural farm in the Penza region of Russia running since 2009.  The farm includes: 500 cows of the Aberdeen-Angus breed; 1000 hectares of land; 500 hectares of pasture; 500 hectares of land for fodder preparation; Feedlot and Meat-processing workshop; Total area of all buildings is 11500 sq.m.  We produce organic beef that is selling to local shops in Penza region as well as in Moscow, and is delivering to our own restaurants under the label "Meat Desire". You can come and taste our burgers right now!

Author: Beef Coin
Title: [ICO] BeefCoin - Integrated production of organic beef from farm to table
Body: There are two types of tokens issued: Main token - BeefCoin (BEEF) and Bonus token - BeefGold (BEEFG).  2,000,000 BEEF tokens for crowdsale. Fixed price: 1 BEEF = 1 USD Token holders get annual dividend 10%, and there will be buyback of 10% issued tokens every year. Token holders can sell their tokens back in any year. So, if you sell back in 1 year, you get 10% profit; if you sell tokens back in 2 years, you get compound profit 21% and so on.  Earlier investors who buy tokens during first 4 weeks of Token Sale Period, also get bonus BeefGold tokens. Bonus tokens provide the right to get 20% share of net profit of our business, additionally to annual fixed dividend described above.  Minimum investment is 100 USD.
